Begin Again starring Keira Knightley, Mark Ruffalo, Adam Levine and James Corden. (formerly Can a Song Save Your Life?)[6] is a 2013 American musical drama film written and directed by John Carney, It had its world premiere at the 2013 Toronto International Film Festival and was released theatrically in July 2014.
